{"id":392999,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/05/网易新闻-贵阳居民楼垮塌-记者相机被副市长指挥/","date":"2015-05-20T14:22:33Z","modified":"2015-05-20T14:22:33Z","title":"网易新闻 | 贵阳居民楼垮塌 记者相机被副市长指挥抢夺","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-393002\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"AQ2G52K200AN0001\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2G52K200AN0001-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-393003\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"AQ2GJJDH00AN0001\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/AQ2GJJDH00AN0001-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>据贵阳市人民政府官方微博消息，因连续降雨山体滑坡造成贵阳市某小区一栋九层高的居民房发生垮塌，倒塌楼房内共35户114位居民。</strong></p>\n<p>截至周三中午12时40分，14人被救出。目前仍有人被困，消防员仍在现场大一堆钢筋及瓦砾中搜救。</p>\n<p>发生垮塌的楼房是贵阳市云岩区头桥社区宏富景苑21栋第4单元。三单元半侧楼损毁严重。</p>\n<p>另据中国央视现场实拍画面显示，垮塌现场一片废墟。</p>\n<p>贵阳市人民政府官微说，相关排查工作正在进行中。截至下午1时30分，已排查26户96人，其中91人安全。有5人未联络上。</p>\n<p>目前，周围居民已被当局紧急疏散。</p>\n<p><strong>来源：BBC中文网</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-393004\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323.jpg\" alt=\"U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323\" width=\"550\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/U11347P1T1D31855951F21DT20150520182323-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@媒老大：贵阳副市长指挥抢夺记者相机。今天上午，贵州省贵阳市区一栋九层民房垮塌，事故发生时有居民正在楼内。赶往采访的新华社记者欧东衢称，他在亮明#新华社记者#身份后，仍被阻挡拍摄，图右工作人员现场指挥：“把他的相机收了。”经了解，指挥抢夺相机者是贵阳市副市长徐昊。</p>\n<p>@新华社欧东衢：记者在亮明新华社记者身份后，仍被阻挡拍摄，图右工作人员现场指挥：“把他的相机收了。”经了解，指挥抢夺相机者是贵阳市副市长徐昊。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[27826,27825,9389,27824]}